Package: xtail
Type: Package
Title: Genome-wide assessment of differential translations with ribosome profiling data
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Zhengtao", "Xiao", email="zhengtao.xiao[at]xjtu.edu.cn",
             role = c("aut","cre")),
      person("Qin", "Zou", role = "aut"),
      person("Yu", "Liu", role = "aut"),
      person("Xuerui", "Yang", role = "aut"),
      person("Rongyao", "Huang", email = "THUhry12[at]163.com", role = "ctb"))
Description: 
    The xtail package is designed to identify genes exhibiting differential 
    translation between two experimental conditions by simultaneously analyzing 
    changes in RNA-seq and ribo-seq data. The estimation of changes in read 
    counts are performed using the DESeq2 package.
